{
  "text": "Hypoxia is involved both directly and indirectly in the induction of EMT, through Twist expression [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , favoring the dissemination of cells from the primary tumor site, while the revertant MET phenotype is important for bone colonization [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
